Syntax: weather
Syntax: weather <"better" | "worse">
Syntax: weather <"month"> <num>
Syntax: weather <"moon"> <num>

Weather displays the present weather conditions as well as a theoretical
prediction about the future.

Immortals can pass the "better" or "worse" parameters to change the weather as
necessary.

The "month" parameter is used to change the current mud month.  <num> should
be 1-12, inclusive.

The "moon" parameter will change the state of the moon.  <num> should be 1-28,
inclusive.

See Also: TIME
Related Topics: GENERAL INFO
